item.dc:creator: @deans1243 deans1243
item.description:
@deans1243 wrote:

he probably doesnt know how thats why he asks.
i got this from my delta source so idk if it will work on pi but you can try

[code] if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“god”) && playerRights >= 1) {
setAnimation(1500);
playerSE = 1501;
playerSEW = 1851;
playerSER = 1851;
playerSEA = 1851;
playerEnergy = 999;

        sendFrame126(playerEnergy + "%", 149);
        sM("God mode turned on, do ::godoff to turn it off.");
        updateRequired = true;
        appearanceUpdateRequired = true;
    } else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("godoff") && playerRights >= 1) {
        sM("God mode turned off.");
        playerSE = 0x328;
        playerSEW = 0x333;
        playerSER = 0x338;
        playerSEA = 0x326;
        playerEnergy = 100;
        playerLevel[3] = getLevelForXP(playerXP[3]);
        sendFrame126(playerEnergy + "%", 149);
        updateRequired = true;
        appearanceUpdateRequired = true;
   }[/code]
